title: Godasadog "Xodó": Rubber Tracks Live
description:
Converse Rubber Tracks recording artists Godasadog were hand picked by night one headliners, Chromeo, to get the party started. Enjoy an amazing performance of their track Xodó.

For more on Converse Rubber Tracks:
http://www.converse.com/rubbertracks

Venue: Cine Joia
